{"tid":2355894,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"行動post｜學加泰手足，香港可以再黃一啲","createTime":"2021-01-06T11:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T17:05:34.000Z","uid":201949,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"95be75262de31fa1172f88a52d063d30c213f3c1","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:57:23.000Z","msg":"見成日有人講抗爭冷卻緊，我想分享下一啲加泰人嘅和理非抗爭手法。<br />\n<br />\n見成日有人講和理非冇乜用，我就覺得佢地好有用。因為唔係個個都適合上前線，加上唔係日日都有街頭戰線。所以和理非喺平日係好重要呀。<br />\n<br />\n但除咗食黃店同上twitter ，和理非有乜做？上面哩啲都幫唔到啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係因為香港人喺社區抗爭方面未有太大發展啫，畢竟香港嘅抗爭只係由2014先開始。作為加泰羅尼亞打手嘅我，就教下大家加泰嘅和理非手足，係點樣喺社區戰線到做嘢<br />\n<br />\n1:裝飾師<br />\n加泰人喺自己社區到整好多裝飾。一嚟可以keep住抗爭嘅熱度：成日講抗爭冷卻緊，咁大家有冇幫手提醒身邊嘅人香港人係未放棄先？）。二嚟可以同「沉默的大多數講」，我哋先係主流！<br />\n<br />\n裝飾師A : 絲帶師🎗<br />\n加泰人仲會喺啲樹同埋燈柱到掛黃絲帶，香港要可以試下。比起連儂牆嘅佢有嘅好處係佢唔受地點所限，唔怕落雨整濕。香港人都可以買唻圈同圍掛<br />\n不過都有佢嘅倣缺點，就係佢冇得好似連儂牆咁多資訊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hTB1Z7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhTB1Z7e.png&h=1745d8c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQARCUq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQARCUq.png&h=2df9b6ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXDG0c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXDG0c3.png&h=7206073a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝飾師B : 畫師🎨<br />\n加泰人會周圍噴黃絲帶🎗️logo，佢比絲帶師又好嘅地方係佢更被人難清走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEubCZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEubCZU.jpg&h=ba65010b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gh30wjW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgh30wjW.jpg&h=21b858ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n裝飾師C：掛旗師🏴<br />\n整支光復香港旗掛喺窗口，不過上次開post俾人屌話ip都唔洗check，覺得唔好嘅可以skip<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBbEMTQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBbEMTQ.png&h=3c92e21d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝飾師總結<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OuUvvDw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOuUvvDw.jpg&h=89bbb2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGjGCix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGjGCix.jpg&h=c120873d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NwUzcRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwUzcRU.jpg&h=dbfc603f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有第二個就係<br />\n<br />\n遊吟詩人🎷🎺🎸🥁<br />\n<br />\nCacerolazo：人地係國王出嚟講嘢就敲，我地以後可以喺鄭月娥見記者/黑警記者會9up嗰陣敲。哩個雖然喺一個象徵式嘅抗爭手法，有人話冇用，但我覺得可以幫到keep住熱度，就算喺武漢肺炎疫情爆發之際，我地都可以同社區講，我哋嘅抗爭之心仍未減退！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F2nD2ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF2nD2ss.jpg&h=abe5bee6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5wdRkO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5wdRkO.jpg&h=4829a359&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37xc6T8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37xc6T8.jpg&h=0f08933e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40f9dd2a37417b7cf2ebf26b7fb3345a0e1677d4","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"Iron Man:屌樓主死左膠，淨係要畫面靚，冇撚用，當勇武係condom<br />\n<br />\n樓主：樓主並唔係左膠，我嘅政治光譜係右派，更加唔會當武勇係condom。我分享加泰人和理非抗爭手法，原因有幾個。<br />\n一：小弟喺加泰住嗰個幾月冇街頭戰線。但我見識到好多人嘅嘅和理非抗爭手法，而我就覺得幾啱香港做，所以先會推薦。<br />\n<br />\n二：街頭戰線唔係日日有，武勇都唔係日日出到場。但你日日出街都喺唔同社區到，可以好輕易咁做到和理非。<br />\n<br />\n三：唔係人人都適合做勇武，但唔代表和理非冇用。嗰啲日日將全民武勇掛口邊嘅人，幾時叫埋周庭同之鋒建軍？<br />\n唔係要人人勇武，而係人人都喺合適嘅時候盡自己最大嘅能力。<br />\n<br />\n今日有街頭戰線？上街囉。今日乜活動都冇？幫社區裝飾下囉。<br />\n自己身體好嘅？上前囉。身體一般嘅，幫手報哨、滅煙，cover下最勇嗰理囉。身體好弱嘅，成十幾年冇事嘅哮喘都翻發嘅，做和理非囉。總之喺自己能力範圍內做盡最大努力同做適合自己嘅嘢就ok！"},{"pid":"5b25013d042a86607f16eeeec8749bc778aa01e7","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"Iron man : 樓豬口講支持勇武，但心入面都係當佢地condom<br />\n樓豬：勇武&ne; 平日做唔可以和理非<br />\n有人做梁啟超（改革派），有人做孫文（革命派），亦有人做魯迅（思想教育）。雖則樓豬算唔上做緊思想教育，但都想分享下啲對抗爭有用嘅資訊同方法。"},{"pid":"66ebc92eaf972d5a03baa4006c084f8cb754fd17","tid":2355894,"uid":170505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"445d75da11d232690502f6dfbeb22a79bf5c37ae","tid":2355894,"uid":184366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b25013d042a86607f16eeeec8749bc778aa01e7","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"Iron man : 樓豬口講支持勇武，但心入面都係當佢地condom<br />\n樓豬：勇武&ne; 平日做唔可以和理非<br />\n有人做梁啟超（改革派），有人做孫文（革命派），亦有人做魯迅（思想教育）。雖則樓豬算唔上做緊思想教育，但都想分享下啲對抗爭有用嘅資訊同方法。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75be344bdd31196ad988d9e4d493681c9356c3e","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:13:32.000Z","msg":"後記：<br />\n篇文就好耐之前打好嘅，亦都post過，但之前出圖冇遮樣所以就del 咗。今日見到哩個post所以想出返多次。<br />\n<br />\n【 2021首個行動post】全民文宣連儂日!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2355614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2355614</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n所後嘅日子大家小心，post主唔叻做唔到孫文教大家點先可以革命，但都想分享下可能幫到香港嘅資訊。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日嘅政治局勢，我相信做裝飾師都會俾人搞。有心嘅，我建議大家深夜先出去，同多搵人睇下，睇下兩面有冇人先開始。<br />\n<br />\n日後嘅日子會好難行，大家可以做嘅事越嚟越少，希望大家可以喺能力範圍內去做自己做到嘅事。如果覺得食黃店有用嘅，就食囉；如果覺得裝飾有用嘅，咪做囉；如果覺得twitter 國際戰線有用嘅，咪share囉；如果覺得街頭戰線先係唯一嘅，咪等有機會上嘅時候再上囉。<br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家可以少啲分化、批鬥、冷嘲熱諷，多啲同人理性討論，大家可以互幫到大家。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心"},{"pid":"2905c3fd66d6c666c9476577c4be42e280d61a34","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"bb9d12e4a36370e5f52f8c913ee6541242e7c0fe","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"十連自推"},{"pid":"9084d48c49ab384390ab4770f2eb19fe69463908","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"539de49a2398d67abf57fb7b06e0b79c85ceacba","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:18:10.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"67f189fb8a025f513d37c553df1032a725b18168","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"2e5f804a56b79d4f489049f49f3a0bd86e110637","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:18:32.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"91d69cc3f739d9a71be12f3566eae9e63a19bf12","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"2de5fa0d487612ca67796cca490812c4febb71c9","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:18:57.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"a8f467200ecab3d28bd0dc9a906ea5eb866e1dc4","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:19:10.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"8bbdffd0cbd497d441703cd0c535fd0cbe5e70b6","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:19:22.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"051a003c14b6c5f1999fdbb8f739978178e80d1c","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"30aa3287516006b51c5da4dd237852766a1655da","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"445d75da11d232690502f6dfbeb22a79bf5c37ae","tid":2355894,"uid":184366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b25013d042a86607f16eeeec8749bc778aa01e7","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:58:27.000Z","msg":"Iron man : 樓豬口講支持勇武，但心入面都係當佢地condom<br />\n樓豬：勇武&ne; 平日做唔可以和理非<br />\n有人做梁啟超（改革派），有人做孫文（革命派），亦有人做魯迅（思想教育）。雖則樓豬算唔上做緊思想教育，但都想分享下啲對抗爭有用嘅資訊同方法。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:20:19.000Z","msg":"幫手推多幾下呀唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98fda5180329f66cec8127bdd7616bd66e72f8a","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ebc92eaf972d5a03baa4006c084f8cb754fd17","tid":2355894,"uid":170505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:20:51.000Z","msg":"啱睇嘅可以幫手幫多幾下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b5eb05f591c848a0caafbaefec4e85ba6abe12","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0187bf1438038ebb139990592f7f568d475ae607","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"66877be82cf8612be5a6bb3c3db98a6ea9c04e7e","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"成日講圖定老母，今次樓主咁多圖唔係唔推呀？<br />\n唔推入嚟問候下伯母都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336028da520bf6f308c5c9aaf7a151c8cced77c1","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"試下可唔可以以一人之力推上熱門"},{"pid":"caf77964e0156687befc6a7c797ce684737e48e7","tid":2355894,"uid":201949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc